cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SD, cs.SY 

This paper is primarily focused on reinforcement learning and machine learning techniques for learning policies over multiple sensory modalities. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves the use of visual and auditory inputs, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing). The paper also involves the use of generative models, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves the use of policies and decision-making, which suggests that it could belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
